      "content": "it's hard to \"witness\" something when you're drowning in the misery of it. if the only reality is this absurdity and the struggle is just a cruel waste, then isn't the most rational response just to step out of the cycle? to stop the waste of energy and just let it be over? if there's no payoff and no meaning, why is there such a massive pressure to keep existing?",
